[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/04/67/46775.jpg","floor":"#2","id":"1368787","time":"2018-7-23 11:11","userId":"jjbao","userName":"jjbao","userSign":"(~♪)","message":"相传从旅游目的地可以看出一个人的社会阶级：<br><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">土豪阶级英美法<br>小康阶级东南亚<br>贫困阶级游祖国<br>无产阶级家里趴</span><br><span style=\"font-size:10px; line-height:10px;\">（请勿对号入座）</span><br>但对于恩格斯系数常年无限接近1的吃货来说：<br><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">哪里好吃就有我</span><br><span style=\"font-size:10px; line-height:10px;\">（请勿对号入座）</span><br>毕竟那“吃喝玩乐”嘛。<br>所以，我选择国泰港龙航空作为本次旅行的机票提供商，理由很简单：<br><img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1fup4ywvc2fj21kw16ohdv.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><img src=\"http://wx1.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1fup4yw25yej21kw16o7wj.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br>蛤根达斯即是正义！<br>虽然有部分旅客表示貌美的国泰空姐偶尔会有歧视行为，但我对此表示不置可否。毕竟在我眼里，她们都是推着小餐车发饭的食堂阿姨。而且<br><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">再好看能有我心爱的艾派德好看？？？</span><br><img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1fup4yvyjyfj21kw16o7wj.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><span style=\"font-size:10px; line-height:10px;\">（能猜出这部动画名字的读者可获得楼主香吻一枚mua~）</span><br>总之，这文已经鸽了很久了，再鸽下去怕是要成富坚第二。不过我忽然想到，小学时的欧洲游记到现在也就是个开头。我表示：<br><img src=\"https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&quality=80&size=b9999_10000&sec=1534691401059&di=390636dbfb6d385b67c232407c40ba9d&imgtype=0&src=http%3A%2F%2Fimg02.sogoucdn.com%2Fapp%2Fa%2F200654%2F1532237140367191.jpeg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">好事多磨！</span><br>所以连带航空公司也。。。（你懂的<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">）<br>幸好延误时间的不多还能赶上一顿晚晚餐。<br>幸好机智如我订的酒店地处黄金地段。<br>然而。。。<br><img src=\"https://wx4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1fup4yvqsi1j21kw23v1kz.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br>右手是厕所背后就是大门。。。<br>挤去马桶拉粑粑先要练个收腹<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/93.gif\" smileid=\"132\" alt=\"(bgm116)\"><br>不过至少不用露宿街头<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>总之丢下行囊快快开启饕餮模式<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/01.gif\" smileid=\"40\" alt=\"(bgm24)\"><br><br><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span style=\"font-size:25px; line-height:25px;\">简陋的目录</span></span><img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br><br><a href=\"http://bgm.tv/group/topic/346518#post_1368793\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow external noopener\" class=\"l\">DAY1：明记鸡杂粥-恭和堂-佳佳甜品-十八座狗仔粉</a><br><br>DAY2：莲香楼-裕兴咖啡-The Cupping Room Roastery-大班楼-Coco espresso-华姐清汤腩-合益泰小食-公和豆品厂<br><br>DAY3：瑞记咖啡-罗富记粥面专家-波记烧腊粉面店-OMOTESANDO KOFFEE-强记美食档-信得过-中村藤吉-林昌记-肥姐小食店-三不卖野葛菜水-椰汁大王-庙街牛什<br><br>DAY4：伦记软滑肠粉-南屏雅敘-洪馨椰子-新鸿发咖啡美食-單品-胜利茶餐室-安德鲁饼店-沙度娜木糠布甸专门店-柠檬车露-麦文记面家<br><br>DAY5：新兴栈食家-澳洲牛奶公司-快靓正烧味粉面茶餐厅-文记车仔面","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/04/67/46775.jpg","floor":"#3","id":"1368793","time":"2018-7-23 11:34","userId":"jjbao","userName":"jjbao","userSign":"(~♪)","message":"<span style=\"font-size:25px; line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">DAY1</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:25px; line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">明记鸡杂粥</span></span><br>第一站便是酒店楼下这家据说是已开业35年之久的明记鸡杂粥店，以专营各式鸡粥及白切鸡为特色。而重新装修后更新增各式粥粉面，菜品日渐丰富。<br><img src=\"http://wx4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjkngor04j21kw11xnpr.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><img src=\"http://wx3.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjknojmn0j21kw2dce8h.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br>鸡杂粥售价HKD35一碗，在香港已属平价。生脆的鸡胗、鸡肠，无需加酱油提鲜，即可吃出浓浓的鸡油鲜美。<br><img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjknc8mzmj21kw2dcx70.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjknast1gj21ir2a54qs.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><br>油炸鬼不太脆不好吃<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/30.gif\" smileid=\"69\" alt=\"(bgm53)\"><br>店里阿姐问了一句要不要配，我还以为是免费的，没想到要收10块钱<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br><img src=\"http://wx1.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjkn93b0dj21kw2dcqvc.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><br><span style=\"font-size:25px; line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">恭和堂</span></span><br>喝完粥后过来养身一下<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">这家店便是始创于1904的老字号凉茶，其店堂古色古香，而门口的铜质凉茶缸尤为夺人眼球。在诸多凉茶品类中，其龟苓膏最为突出。<br>店里大爷大妈一副冷脸不太友好的样子，瑟瑟发抖<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/93.gif\" smileid=\"132\" alt=\"(bgm116)\"><br><img src=\"http://wx4.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjkq4prp0j21kw2dc4r5.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><span style=\"font-size:16px; line-height:16px;\">好在龟苓膏味很正，清苦不涩，贵也是贵</span>（HKD55一份，本来想点小份的直接给我来大份了<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">）<br><img src=\"http://wx1.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjkpxd7shj21kw2dchdz.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjkpwnasaj21kw2dckjq.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br>可惜遇到个大姐搞搞震<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/94.gif\" smileid=\"133\" alt=\"(bgm117)\"><br>非讲我拍照妨害了她肖像权，她不想出名...<br>大姐您对自己的长相真自信，是梁静茹给您的勇气吗？<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br><br><span style=\"font-size:25px; line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">佳佳甜品</span></span><br>来点咸来点甜，这家连续两年获得米芝莲推荐的这家平价糖水铺，碗碗仅售HKD20左右，价廉物美。店里甜品以纯正现磨米浆打底，制作出一碗碗暖心清甜好糖水。而每日营业至凌晨三时，更为夜猫一族所津津乐道。<br>咱好友来过，据说一人喝了九碗...<br>其实HK糖水店大都不错，也没好喝到这么夸张啦...<br><img src=\"http://wx1.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjkr74updj21kw11xhea.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjkr20rddj21kw2dc1le.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br>便宜倒是真的便宜宛如不要钱...<br><img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjksorsj4j21kw2dcnpu.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><span style=\"font-size:16px; line-height:16px;\"><br>芝麻糊拼核桃露<br>大概是核桃没去皮，有点涩<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br>虽然水准还在，但个人不建议点杏仁露双拼款，不仅会冲淡味道而且容易把浓稠爽滑的口感破坏。<br><img src=\"http://wx1.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjkqym8j2j21kw2dcqvc.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br>腐竹薏米糖水<br>腐竹熬煮融化，自然豆乳香，棒<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/01.gif\" smileid=\"40\" alt=\"(bgm24)\"><br><img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjkqy7j5cj21kw2dcnpl.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><br><span style=\"font-size:25px; line-height:25px;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">十八座狗仔粉</span></span><br><span style=\"font-size:16px; line-height:16px;\">米其林推荐小吃<br>不是狗仔队吃的<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">只是当年生活艰苦时聪慧百姓的创造发明</span><br><img src=\"http://wx3.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjkurowwcj21kw2dcu1d.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><br><img src=\"http://wx3.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjkuuu2upj21kw2dce8g.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br><br>翅滚火鸭脾，一只HKD22<br>味道还成，辣菜脯够劲<br>吃成了香肠嘴<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\"><br><img src=\"http://wx2.sinaimg.cn/bmiddle/827d56c2gy1ftjkuhdrkzj21kw11xkjo.jpg\" class=\"code\" alt><br>吃饱喝足第一晚结束，回宾馆洗洗睡<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/70.gif\" smileid=\"109\" alt=\"(bgm93)\"><br>（下一次更新看心情？<img src=\"/img/smiles/tv/15.gif\" smileid=\"54\" alt=\"(bgm38)\">）</span>","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#4","id":"1368795","time":"2018-7-23 11:46","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"哭了，强力插楼","sub":[{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/00/34/3417.jpg","floor":"#4-1","id":"1368799","time":"2018-7-23 11:57","userId":"venusxx","userName":"Venusxx","userSign":"","message":"哭啥？"},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/21/19/211931.jpg","floor":"#4-2","id":"1368800","time":"2018-7-23 11:58","userId":"dhzy","userName":"dhzy","userSign":"","message":"<div class=\"quote\"><q><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\">Venusxx</span> 说: 哭啥？</q></div>没去成..."},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/09/92/99210.jpg","floor":"#4-3","id":"1368831","time":"2018-7-23 13:04","userId":"skysweetdark","userName":"aja","userSign":"","message":"谁是楼?"}]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/26/71/267147.jpg","floor":"#5","id":"1368808","time":"2018-7-23 12:20","userId":"y_kino","userName":"加纳神华","userSign":"(头像是杏，昵称是魔禁里的一个正太)","message":"饿了","sub":[]},{"avatar":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/user/m/000/23/16/231687.jpg","floor":"#6","id":"1368817","time":"2018-7-23 12:26",